00:22:30,791 --> 00:22:31,958
This can't be true.

526
00:22:32,041 --> 00:22:34,041
Hey, Takki, what's wrong?

527
00:22:34,125 --> 00:22:36,041
-Look at this.
-Huh?

528
00:22:36,125 --> 00:22:38,500
Whoa, they're going
crazy over it!

529
00:22:38,583 --> 00:22:39,875
"Phantasm...

530
00:22:39,958 --> 00:22:42,125
FES's real name is Ayase...

531
00:22:42,208 --> 00:22:43,791
She was previously
hospitalized

532
00:22:43,875 --> 00:22:45,416
due to psychiatric problems."

533
00:22:45,500 --> 00:22:46,708
"AHM...

534
00:22:46,791 --> 00:22:48,416
Arkheart Medical Group...

535
00:22:48,500 --> 00:22:51,000
It's a longstanding
specialized medical facility

536
00:22:51,083 --> 00:22:53,625
which only treats
serious mental cases."

537
00:22:53,708 --> 00:22:55,375
Ayase's been there, too?

538
00:22:55,458 --> 00:22:57,666
Hurry up...
You must find it...

539
00:22:57,750 --> 00:22:59,875
If you can find your
sword you will be saved.

540
00:22:59,958 --> 00:23:02,666
I wonder if I can really
believe the things she says.

541
00:23:03,916 --> 00:23:05,583
Damn... Stupid
phone scared me.

542
00:23:05,666 --> 00:23:07,375
That's exactly why
I didn't want one.

543
00:23:07,458 --> 00:23:08,708
Well, pick it up.

544
00:23:08,791 --> 00:23:10,625
It's probably
just Nanami...

545
00:23:10,708 --> 00:23:12,000
Hello. What?

546
00:23:18,500 --> 00:23:19,375
Who is this?

547
00:23:21,083 --> 00:23:23,000
The General...?

548
00:23:23,083 --> 00:23:24,666
Seira baby,
what should I do?

549
00:23:24,750 --> 00:23:25,750
Should I answer?

550
00:23:25,833 --> 00:23:27,000
You can ignore him,
you know...

551
00:23:27,083 --> 00:23:28,208
Just hang up.

552
00:23:28,291 --> 00:23:29,291
Oh, yeah...

553
00:23:29,375 --> 00:23:31,166
I could definitely
just hang up, huh?

554
00:23:35,583 --> 00:23:36,916
What's that?

555
00:23:39,666 --> 00:23:40,958
Takki.

556
00:24:01,333 --> 00:24:02,416
Taku.

557
00:24:17,708 --> 00:24:19,916
Hello?

558
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:22,583
Yes, and who is
this exactly...?

559
00:24:22,666 --> 00:24:24,083
Oh... I'm fine...

560
00:24:24,166 --> 00:24:26,416
No, everything's
okay, it's just...

561
00:24:26,500 --> 00:24:28,125
I'm sorry, say that again?

562
00:24:28,208 --> 00:24:29,625
But that can't
be possible...!

563
00:24:29,708 --> 00:24:31,000
Because...

564
00:24:31,083 --> 00:24:33,625
Because actually
I'm the one who...

565
00:24:33,708 --> 00:24:35,500
Get away from the windows!

566
00:24:35,583 --> 00:24:36,916
Yes...

567
00:24:37,000 --> 00:24:38,916
Yes...

568
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:40,583
She's my sister...

569
00:24:40,666 --> 00:24:42,458
Oh, okay...

570
00:24:42,541 --> 00:24:44,375
Okay, thank you very much.

571
00:25:07,375 --> 00:25:13,083
[Music]

572
00:26:43,666 --> 00:26:45,333
Those eyes...

573
00:26:45,416 --> 00:26:46,708
Whose are they?

